cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SI

The paper deals with the use of deep neural networks for speech synthesis from ultrasound video input. This involves image processing, speech recognition, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image processing, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision), and the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
